31:40.000 --> 31:41.625
♪ Ah ♪

31:41.708 --> 31:45.458
- [whistling]
- ♪ When the twilight is gone ♪

31:45.541 --> 31:47.541
- ♪ Gone ♪
- [indistinct shouting]

31:47.625 --> 31:50.541
- ♪ You come into my heart ♪
- [Rhett] Now come on.

31:50.625 --> 31:52.458
♪ Ah ♪

31:52.541 --> 31:57.291
♪ And here in my heart
you will stay ♪

31:57.375 --> 31:59.958
♪ While ♪

32:00.041 --> 32:06.500
♪ I pray ♪

32:06.541 --> 32:08.125
[Rhett] Come on!

32:08.208 --> 32:12.541
♪ My prayer ♪

32:12.625 --> 32:15.958
♪ Is to linger with you ♪

32:16.041 --> 32:17.541
[Royal] Hup, hup, hup, hup.

32:17.625 --> 32:18.875
[whistles]

32:20.500 --> 32:24.625
- ♪ At the end of the day ♪
- [clicking tongue]

32:27.333 --> 32:30.250
- Hup, hup, hup, hup. Hup.
- ♪ In a dream that's divine ♪

32:34.125 --> 32:39.500
♪ My prayer ♪

32:39.583 --> 32:43.666
- ♪ Is a rapture in blue ♪
- [horse neighs]

32:46.791 --> 32:51.833
♪ With the world far away ♪

32:53.375 --> 32:57.291
♪ And your lips close to mine...

32:57.375 --> 32:59.333
Where's he going?

32:59.416 --> 33:02.000
Off his rocker, you ask me.

33:02.083 --> 33:07.000
♪ Tonight ♪

33:07.083 --> 33:12.125
♪ While our hearts are aglow ♪

33:16.083 --> 33:20.291
- ♪ Oh, tell the words ♪
- [lowing]

33:20.375 --> 33:26.416
- [neighs]
- ♪ That I'm longing to know ♪

33:27.416 --> 33:30.541
♪ At the end of ♪

33:30.625 --> 33:37.625
♪ My prayer ♪

33:37.708 --> 33:41.291
♪ Do-do-do-do,
do-do-do-do, do ♪♪

33:41.375 --> 33:43.375
[insects trilling]

33:50.875 --> 33:53.041
♪ ♪

33:57.875 --> 33:59.375
[horse whinnies softly]

34:08.416 --> 34:10.416
♪ ♪

34:38.833 --> 34:41.416
[Autumn] What are you
looking for?

34:41.500 --> 34:43.291
[rodent squeaking]

34:43.375 --> 34:45.583
[Royal] I'd ask you the same.

34:50.333 --> 34:52.833
Want you off my land.

34:52.916 --> 34:54.041
No, you don't.

34:54.125 --> 34:56.291
And why is that?

34:56.375 --> 34:59.416
'Cause you need me to keep
a hell of a lot of secrets,

34:59.500 --> 35:02.375
least of which is the fact that
you threw a body into a hole.

35:02.458 --> 35:03.458
So did you.

35:03.541 --> 35:05.750
But you came back.

35:07.541 --> 35:08.666
How?

35:17.458 --> 35:19.000
What's your real name?

35:19.083 --> 35:20.750
Autumn.

35:20.833 --> 35:23.000
- What's your last name?
- Rivers.

35:23.083 --> 35:25.375
How'd you get all your money?

35:25.458 --> 35:27.000
Trust fund.

35:27.083 --> 35:28.875
Fuck you. You have
an interest in mining?

35:28.958 --> 35:31.291
- Mining?
- Mm-hmm. Drilling.

35:31.375 --> 35:33.166
Mining. You have an interest
in mining?

35:33.250 --> 35:34.541
No.

35:34.625 --> 35:36.208
- You work for the government?
- [chuckles] No.

35:36.291 --> 35:37.541
- Have you ever?
- No.

35:37.625 --> 35:40.000
You ever been involved
in a cult?

35:40.083 --> 35:41.208
Yes.

35:41.291 --> 35:43.666
What does the color yellow
mean to you?

35:43.750 --> 35:46.583
- What does the color yellow
mean to you?
- I'm thinking. Why?

35:46.666 --> 35:48.791
- What's the color yellow...
- Power.

35:48.875 --> 35:50.500
- You ever kill anyone?
- No, have you?

35:50.583 --> 35:52.125
Was that you that did that?

35:52.208 --> 35:54.125
Were you trying to kill me
when you threw me in?

35:54.208 --> 35:55.166
[Autumn] No.

35:55.250 --> 35:56.458
My turn.

35:57.458 --> 36:00.041
What do you remember
from your childhood?

36:02.041 --> 36:04.250
Do you remember anything
before the age of nine?

36:04.333 --> 36:06.083
Why?

36:06.166 --> 36:09.125
'Cause I didn't
until I got here.

36:11.666 --> 36:13.875
Do you believe in fate?

36:18.041 --> 36:19.500
Something brought me here.

36:19.583 --> 36:22.333
What would that be?

36:22.416 --> 36:24.416
That's what you're gonna help me
figure out.

36:25.416 --> 36:27.333
Something's happening here.

36:27.416 --> 36:29.000
Something bigger
than you and me,

36:29.083 --> 36:31.625
and we're the only two people
that know about it.

36:31.708 --> 36:34.083
And we can help each other
understand this.

36:34.166 --> 36:36.458
- We don't have to be afraid.
- [horse snorts]

36:38.500 --> 36:39.541
What did you see in there?

36:39.625 --> 36:41.625
♪ ♪

36:56.541 --> 36:58.541
♪ ♪

37:02.916 --> 37:04.208
[grunts]

37:07.083 --> 37:09.083
♪ ♪

37:31.291 --> 37:33.375
♪ ♪

